Pre-Game Insights: Cyprus and Latvia struggled in Euro 2024 qualifying
Cyprus finished bottom of their group, while Latvia finished with three points
Neither nation has shown much to get excited about over the past 12 months
Miscellaneous Highlights: Pieros Sotiriou is back at Ketsbaia's disposal for this encounter and is in contention to start
Antonijs Cernomordijs is a late withdrawal from the squad due to injury
Others: The match ended in a 1-1 draw
The match was played on March 21, 2024, at 5pm UK at Makareio Stadio in Cyprus
